      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in poor condition. The vehicle has significant wear throughout \u2014 the interior shows notable damage to upholstery and trim surfaces, with visible staining and deterioration on high-contact areas. The exterior has multiple scratches, dents, or other cosmetic damage. Mechanical issues are present and the car will likely require repairs before reliable daily use. Sold as-is.",
