    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we believe in full transparency about what that means for you as a buyer. The exterior shows visible signs of regular use \u2014 you can expect moderate scratches, some paint fading in areas, and minor dents here and there. The interior is functional but shows wear on the seats, trim, and surfaces consistent with its age and mileage. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs down the road. This is a practical, no-frills option for someone looking for dependable transportation at an honest price \u2014 not a showroom car, but a solid everyday driver priced accordingly.",
